smtp-benchmark installation instructions

1) Please take a look at the Makefiles in smtpsend/ and smtpsink/
   and adapt them to your needs beore using them. 

2) enter make in the smtp-benchmark directory or in one
   of it's subdirectories (smtpsend, smtpsink) if you only
   need that component.
   
3) as root, enter make install.  This will install smtpsend, smtpsink
   and the manual pages in your system.
   
